data.description: Discover the allure of 466 Crabapple Pl, Macon, Georgia, a captivating residence built in 2003. Boasting a generous 1828 square feet of living space on a 0.23-acre lot, this home presents four spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, ideal for a growing family or gracious hosting.    Noteworthy attributes include an attached garage for secure vehicle storage and potential extra space, along with a cozy fireplace that imparts warmth and charm on cooler nights. Beyond its well-maintained interiors, this property enjoys a prime location, combining functionality with comfort. Seize the opportunity to call this must-see property your new home - a perfect blend of space and convenience awaits.
